  "texts": [
    "In this context, we are particularly interested in plant leaf detection and classification, specifically in differentiating between healthy and diseased examples.",
    "To perform, there is a need to know about the classification and detection algorithms of ML and DL.",
    "To understand AI's involvement in this domain, it's essential to realize that machine learning is a subset of AI.",
    "ML aims to allow computers to learn from experience (Verma, 2023).",
    "Currently, we come across various subtypes within the ML domain, each suited to different learning scenarios."
  ]
}